          <Rectangle Name="Rectangle2">
            <ReportItems>
              <Textbox Name="Textbox17">
                <CanGrow>true</CanGrow>
                <KeepTogether>true</KeepTogether>
                <Paragraphs>
                  <Paragraph>
                    <TextRuns>
                      <TextRun>
                        <Value>                                                                                                     General</Value>
                        <Style>
                          <FontStyle>Normal</FontStyle>
                          <FontFamily>Segoe UI</FontFamily>
                          <FontSize>8pt</FontSize>
                          <FontWeight>Bold</FontWeight>
                          <TextDecoration>None</TextDecoration>
                          <Color>#000000</Color>
                        </Style>
                      </TextRun>
                      <TextRun>
                        <Value xml:space="preserve"> </Value>
                        <Style>
                          <FontStyle>Normal</FontStyle>
                          <FontFamily>Segoe UI</FontFamily>
                          <FontSize>8pt</FontSize>
                          <FontWeight>Normal</FontWeight>
                          <TextDecoration>None</TextDecoration>
                          <Color>#000000</Color>
                        </Style>
                      </TextRun>
                      <TextRun>
                        <Value>Terms &amp; Conditions </Value>
                        <Style>
                          <FontStyle>Normal</FontStyle>
                          <FontFamily>Segoe UI</FontFamily>
                          <FontSize>8pt</FontSize>
                          <FontWeight>Bold</FontWeight>
                          <TextDecoration>None</TextDecoration>
                          <Color>#000000</Color>
                        </Style>
                      </TextRun>
                    </TextRuns>
                    <Style />
                  </Paragraph>
                  <Paragraph>
                    <TextRuns>
                      <TextRun>
                        <Value />
                        <Style>
                          <FontStyle>Normal</FontStyle>
                          <FontFamily>Segoe UI</FontFamily>
                          <FontSize>8pt</FontSize>
                          <FontWeight>Normal</FontWeight>
                          <TextDecoration>None</TextDecoration>
                          <Color>#000000</Color>
                        </Style>
                      </TextRun>
                    </TextRuns>
                    <Style />
                  </Paragraph>
                  <Paragraph>
                    <TextRuns>
                      <TextRun>
                        <Value>1. Delivery:</Value>
                        <Style>
                          <FontStyle>Normal</FontStyle>
                          <FontFamily>Segoe UI</FontFamily>
                          <FontSize>8pt</FontSize>
                          <FontWeight>Bold</FontWeight>
                          <TextDecoration>None</TextDecoration>
                          <Color>#000000</Color>
                        </Style>
                      </TextRun>
                      <TextRun>
                        <Value> Time of delivery is and shall remain the essence of this P.O. Default in delivery caused force majeure that are beyond Supplier's control shall not make Supplier liable therefore, provided Supplier immediately notifies Buyer of said event and the estimated delay in delivery. Buyer shall have the right to cancel all or any portion of this P.O. which has not been delivered on time. Acceptance by buyer of a late delivery of either a whole or a part of P.O. shall not constitute a waiver of its claim for damage caused it by the late delivery nor its rights to cancel the remaining portion of the P.O. if deliveries are behind the schedule; Buyer may request Supplier to ship by premium freights to cover up for the delay through flights or trains or modes thereof. In such event, the Supplier shall make deliveries using premium modes and Supplier shall pay the difference between the freight by normal mode and premium mode. </Value>
                        <Style>
                          <FontStyle>Normal</FontStyle>
                          <FontFamily>Segoe UI</FontFamily>
                          <FontSize>8pt</FontSize>
                          <FontWeight>Normal</FontWeight>
                          <TextDecoration>None</TextDecoration>
                          <Color>#000000</Color>
                        </Style>
                      </TextRun>
                    </TextRuns>
                    <Style />
                  </Paragraph>
                  <Paragraph>
                    <TextRuns>
                      <TextRun>
                        <Value>               In case of Service PO the invoices should be submitted immediately after the completion of the work. </Value>
                        <Style>
                          <FontStyle>Normal</FontStyle>
                          <FontFamily>Segoe UI</FontFamily>
                          <FontSize>8pt</FontSize>
                          <FontWeight>Normal</FontWeight>
                          <TextDecoration>None</TextDecoration>
                          <Color>#000000</Color>
                        </Style>
                      </TextRun>
                    </TextRuns>
                    <Style />
                  </Paragraph>
                  <Paragraph>
                    <TextRuns>
                      <TextRun>
                        <Value>               Deliveries shall be made in type and quantities as specified in this order. Buyer will not be liable to pay for any excess deliveries made and may return the excess material at the supplier’s cost. </Value>
                        <Style>
                          <FontStyle>Normal</FontStyle>
                          <FontFamily>Segoe UI</FontFamily>
                          <FontSize>8pt</FontSize>
                          <FontWeight>Normal</FontWeight>
                          <TextDecoration>None</TextDecoration>
                          <Color>#000000</Color>
                        </Style>
                      </TextRun>
                    </TextRuns>
                    <Style />
                  </Paragraph>
                  <Paragraph>
                    <TextRuns>
                      <TextRun>
                        <Value>              Unless specified otherwise, Supplier will bear all the costs of delivery and insurance in transit till it reaches Buyer’s destination. </Value>
                        <Style>
                          <FontStyle>Normal</FontStyle>
                          <FontFamily>Segoe UI</FontFamily>
                          <FontSize>8pt</FontSize>
                          <FontWeight>Normal</FontWeight>
                          <TextDecoration>None</TextDecoration>
                          <Color>#000000</Color>
                        </Style>
                      </TextRun>
                    </TextRuns>
                    <Style />
                  </Paragraph>
                  <Paragraph>
                    <TextRuns>
                      <TextRun>
                        <Value>              All the goods delivered should be accompanied by a Supplier invoice detailing the reference PO number, the description and quantity of the goods, rates, barcodes or advance shipment notification numbers and any other information requested by the buyer. </Value>
                        <Style>
                          <FontStyle>Normal</FontStyle>
                          <FontFamily>Segoe UI</FontFamily>
                          <FontSize>8pt</FontSize>
                          <FontWeight>Normal</FontWeight>
                          <TextDecoration>None</TextDecoration>
                          <Color>#000000</Color>
                        </Style>
                      </TextRun>
                    </TextRuns>
                    <Style />
                  </Paragraph>
                  <Paragraph>
                    <TextRuns>
                      <TextRun>
                        <Value>             Supplier should also provide the self- inspection report covering the physical and performance aspects of the goods supplied or provide the copy of such test reports from an authorised third party. </Value>
                        <Style>
                          <FontStyle>Normal</FontStyle>
                          <FontFamily>Segoe UI</FontFamily>
                          <FontSize>8pt</FontSize>
                          <FontWeight>Normal</FontWeight>
                          <TextDecoration>None</TextDecoration>
                          <Color>#000000</Color>
                        </Style>
                      </TextRun>
                    </TextRuns>
                    <Style />
                  </Paragraph>
                  <Paragraph>
                    <TextRuns>
                      <TextRun>
                        <Value>             If the Goods are not delivered or the Services are not performed on the due date then, without prejudice to any other remedy, the Buyer shall be entitled to deduct from the Price or (if the Buyer has paid the Price) to claim from the Seller by way of liquidated damages for delay one (1) per cent of the Price for every week's delay, up to a maximum of ten (10) percent </Value>
                        <Style>
                          <FontStyle>Normal</FontStyle>
                          <FontFamily>Segoe UI</FontFamily>
                          <FontSize>8pt</FontSize>
                          <FontWeight>Normal</FontWeight>
                          <TextDecoration>None</TextDecoration>
                          <Color>#000000</Color>
                        </Style>
                      </TextRun>
                    </TextRuns>
                    <Style />
                  </Paragraph>
                  <Paragraph>
                    <TextRuns>
                      <TextRun>
                        <Value>2. </Value>
                        <Style>
                          <FontStyle>Normal</FontStyle>
                          <FontFamily>Segoe UI</FontFamily>
                          <FontSize>8pt</FontSize>
                          <FontWeight>Normal</FontWeight>
                          <TextDecoration>None</TextDecoration>
                          <Color>#000000</Color>
                        </Style>
                      </TextRun>
                      <TextRun>
                        <Value>Tax Invoice: </Value>
                        <Style>
                          <FontStyle>Normal</FontStyle>
                          <FontFamily>Segoe UI</FontFamily>
                          <FontSize>8pt</FontSize>
                          <FontWeight>Bold</FontWeight>
                          <TextDecoration>None</TextDecoration>
                          <Color>#000000</Color>
                        </Style>
                      </TextRun>
                      <TextRun>
                        <Value>All the Tax Invoices will be submitted in hard copy with the duplicate copies of respective Purchase Order/ Work Order. HSN/SAC should be mentioned in the Tax Invoice.</Value>
                        <Style>
                          <FontStyle>Normal</FontStyle>
                          <FontFamily>Segoe UI</FontFamily>
                          <FontSize>8pt</FontSize>
                          <FontWeight>Normal</FontWeight>
                          <TextDecoration>None</TextDecoration>
                          <Color>#000000</Color>
                        </Style>
                      </TextRun>
                    </TextRuns>
                    <Style />
                  </Paragraph>
                  <Paragraph>
                    <TextRuns>
                      <TextRun>
                        <Value>3. TDS:</Value>
                        <Style>
                          <FontStyle>Normal</FontStyle>
                          <FontFamily>Segoe UI</FontFamily>
                          <FontSize>8pt</FontSize>
                          <FontWeight>Bold</FontWeight>
                          <TextDecoration>None</TextDecoration>
                          <Color>#000000</Color>
                        </Style>
                      </TextRun>
                      <TextRun>
                        <Value> All payments shall be subject to TDS deductions. </Value>
                        <Style>
                          <FontStyle>Normal</FontStyle>
                          <FontFamily>Segoe UI</FontFamily>
                          <FontSize>8pt</FontSize>
                          <FontWeight>Normal</FontWeight>
                          <TextDecoration>None</TextDecoration>
                          <Color>#000000</Color>
                        </Style>
                      </TextRun>
                    </TextRuns>
                    <Style />
                  </Paragraph>
                  <Paragraph>
                    <TextRuns>
                      <TextRun>
                        <Value>4. GST:</Value>
                        <Style>
                          <FontStyle>Normal</FontStyle>
                          <FontFamily>Segoe UI</FontFamily>
                          <FontSize>8pt</FontSize>
                          <FontWeight>Bold</FontWeight>
                          <TextDecoration>None</TextDecoration>
                          <Color>#000000</Color>
                        </Style>
                      </TextRun>
                      <TextRun>
                        <Value> GST should reflect in GST portal as per scheduled timeline. </Value>
                        <Style>
                          <FontStyle>Normal</FontStyle>
                          <FontFamily>Segoe UI</FontFamily>
                          <FontSize>8pt</FontSize>
                          <FontWeight>Normal</FontWeight>
                          <TextDecoration>None</TextDecoration>
                          <Color>#000000</Color>
                        </Style>
                      </TextRun>
                    </TextRuns>
                    <Style />
                  </Paragraph>
                  <Paragraph>
                    <TextRuns>
                      <TextRun>
                        <Value>5. Termination:</Value>
                        <Style>
                          <FontStyle>Normal</FontStyle>
                          <FontFamily>Segoe UI</FontFamily>
                          <FontSize>8pt</FontSize>
                          <FontWeight>Bold</FontWeight>
                          <TextDecoration>None</TextDecoration>
                          <Color>#000000</Color>
                        </Style>
                      </TextRun>
                      <TextRun>
                        <Value xml:space="preserve"> </Value>
                        <Style>
                          <FontStyle>Normal</FontStyle>
                          <FontFamily>Segoe UI</FontFamily>
                          <FontSize>8pt</FontSize>
                          <FontWeight>Normal</FontWeight>
                          <TextDecoration>None</TextDecoration>
                          <Color>#000000</Color>
                        </Style>
                      </TextRun>
                      <TextRun>
                        <Value>=First(Fields!CompanyName.Value, "DataSet_Result")</Value>
                        <Style>
                          <FontFamily>Segoe UI</FontFamily>
                          <FontSize>8pt</FontSize>
                          <FontWeight>Normal</FontWeight>
                        </Style>
                      </TextRun>
                      <TextRun>
                        <Value> reserves the right to terminate the contract with 15 days’ written notice for non-performance, breach of contract, safety violations, insolvency, or failure to meet quality standards. Upon termination, </Value>
                        <Style>
                          <FontStyle>Normal</FontStyle>
                          <FontFamily>Segoe UI</FontFamily>
                          <FontSize>8pt</FontSize>
                          <FontWeight>Normal</FontWeight>
                          <TextDecoration>None</TextDecoration>
                          <Color>#000000</Color>
                        </Style>
                      </TextRun>
                      <TextRun>
                        <Value>=First(Fields!CompanyName.Value, "DataSet_Result")</Value>
                        <Style>
                          <FontFamily>Segoe UI</FontFamily>
                          <FontSize>8pt</FontSize>
                          <FontWeight>Normal</FontWeight>
                        </Style>
                      </TextRun>
                      <TextRun>
                        <Value> shall have the right to take possession of materials, tools, and incomplete work at the site.</Value>
                        <Style>
                          <FontStyle>Normal</FontStyle>
                          <FontFamily>Segoe UI</FontFamily>
                          <FontSize>8pt</FontSize>
                          <FontWeight>Normal</FontWeight>
                          <TextDecoration>None</TextDecoration>
                          <Color>#000000</Color>
                        </Style>
                      </TextRun>
                    </TextRuns>
                    <Style />
                  </Paragraph>
                  <Paragraph>
                    <TextRuns>
                      <TextRun>
                        <Value>6. Dispute Resolution:</Value>
                        <Style>
                          <FontStyle>Normal</FontStyle>
                          <FontFamily>Segoe UI</FontFamily>
                          <FontSize>8pt</FontSize>
                          <FontWeight>Bold</FontWeight>
                          <TextDecoration>None</TextDecoration>
                          <Color>#000000</Color>
                        </Style>
                      </TextRun>
                      <TextRun>
                        <Value> Any dispute arising out of or in connection with this Purchase Order shall be resolved amicably through mutual discussion. If unresolved, the dispute shall be referred to arbitration under the Arbitration and Conciliation Act, 1996. The venue of arbitration shall be </Value>
                        <Style>
                          <FontStyle>Normal</FontStyle>
                          <FontFamily>Segoe UI</FontFamily>
                          <FontSize>8pt</FontSize>
                          <FontWeight>Normal</FontWeight>
                          <TextDecoration>None</TextDecoration>
                          <Color>#000000</Color>
                        </Style>
                      </TextRun>
                      <TextRun>
                        <Value>=First(Fields!ComCity.Value, "DataSet_Result")</Value>
                        <Style>
                          <FontStyle>Normal</FontStyle>
                          <FontFamily>Segoe UI</FontFamily>
                          <FontSize>8pt</FontSize>
                          <FontWeight>Normal</FontWeight>
                          <TextDecoration>None</TextDecoration>
                          <Color>#000000</Color>
                        </Style>
                      </TextRun>
                      <TextRun>
                        <Value>, and language shall be English. </Value>
                        <Style>
                          <FontStyle>Normal</FontStyle>
                          <FontFamily>Segoe UI</FontFamily>
                          <FontSize>8pt</FontSize>
                          <FontWeight>Normal</FontWeight>
                          <TextDecoration>None</TextDecoration>
                          <Color>#000000</Color>
                        </Style>
                      </TextRun>
                    </TextRuns>
                    <Style />
                  </Paragraph>
                  <Paragraph>
                    <TextRuns>
                      <TextRun>
                        <Value>7. Force Majeure:</Value>
                        <Style>
                          <FontStyle>Normal</FontStyle>
                          <FontFamily>Segoe UI</FontFamily>
                          <FontSize>8pt</FontSize>
                          <FontWeight>Bold</FontWeight>
                          <TextDecoration>None</TextDecoration>
                          <Color>#000000</Color>
                        </Style>
